        "Title": "Blame The Chef!",
        "Location": "LOCATION_BANGKOK_ZIKA",
        "PublicId": "116738713787",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Bangkok/scene_zika.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository d20d6e22-2ede-4e6d-b79c-25f225328f14).Image",
        "Description": "Good Afternoon 47,\r\rOur client requests the framing of Tharn Srisai, a renowned chef currently working at the Himmapan Hotel.\r\rAccording to our client, chef Srisai was involved in the mysterious death of the client&apos;s son who worked at the same establishment as part of the kitchen staff back in 2018.\r\rFrame the chef by eliminating the other kitchen staff members using the chef&apos;s trademark Kitchen Knifes. But remember that the framing will only work if you remain unseen.\r\rGood luck.",
